@@TJvFormButton.Glyph
Description:
This property is the image showed in the caption area. There are some samples in the Image directory of the JVCL. The image should have a dimension of 14*11 or 11*8, or similar dimensions.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormButton.OnClick
Description:
This event occurs when the user clicks the button.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormButton.PopupMenu
Description:
This property is the popup menu showed when the user right clicks the button

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormButton.RightMargin
Description:
This property is the distance from the right border of the form to the right part of the button. Use this property to adapt the position of the button following other buttons already present.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormButton.SystemGlyph
Description:
This property is a list of pre defined bitmaps available in the operating system.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormButton.Visible
Description:
This property is the visibility of the button. If this property is true, the button is visible, if not he is hided.

